show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा 
https://links.kukufm.com/UnqWXw
show.description: Simran, a terminally ill girl trapped in a toxic marriage, decides to stage her own farewell with a haunting photoshoot — for her funeral. But secrets unravel fast: a loveless marriage built on blackmail, a sinister stepsister with hidden motives, and a painful past that refuses to die. As Simran battles betrayal, illness, and emotional abuse, she discovers unexpected strength — and one last chance at truth, love, and redemption, one last kiss!
